<div class="banner-container">
  <div class="page-banner banner-image-private">
    <h1 class="page-title title-charity">PRIVATE QUIZZES</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
    <h3>FOR ALL YOU PARTY ANIMALS</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="d-flex">
    <div class="text-bubble text-bubble-yellow col-9 col-md-8 col-lg-8">
      <p>
        Looking to throw a party and need the perfect ice breaker to get things going?
        There’s nothing like a fantastic quiz to get things really cooking!
      </p>
      <p class="empty-line"></p>
      <p>
        We’ve hosted quizzes at weddings, birthday parties, floating down the Thames,
        even at a funeral. If you want to give your private function some real pop,
        drop us a line.
      </p>
      <p class="empty-line"></p>
      <p>
        Contact us for rates and further details.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
      <%= image_tag "private/private_lightbulb.jpg", class: "img-fluid" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="dividing-line-black">

<div class="container private-virtual">
  <div class="text-bubble text-bubble-yellow">
    <h3>VIRTUAL</h3>
    <p>
      Just because your mates are spread across the world is absolutely no reason why
      you can’t enjoy a good quiz. We have hosted huge events of well over a 200
      people on Zoom and lockdown meant we had plenty of time to hone the event to a
      fine art!
    </p>
    <p class="empty-line"></p>
    <p>
      All you need is a computer and a camera, and away we go.
      We also have options of hybrid quizzes where half the contestants are there in
      person, the other half playing online.
    </p>
    <p class="empty-line"></p>
    <p>
      For more information, please <%= link_to "contact us", contact_us_path %>.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<%= image_tag "private/12.jpg", class: "private-dogs-image", alt: "a group of dogs enjoying a party with balloons" %>
